
                    drop table if exists gb_2012_05_15_tousu;
                    create table gb_2012_05_15_tousu engine=myisam  select * from gb_common_201205151200 where 1<>1;


                    DROP PROCEDURE IF EXISTS `sp_Check_Table`; 
                    create procedure sp_check_table (IN p_tablename varchar(50))
                    begin
                      select count(1) from information_schema.tables where table_name = p_tablename into @cnt;
                      if @cnt != 0 then 
                        INSERT into gb_2012_05_15_tousu select * from  gb_common_201205152330 where IMSI='460006164215696';
                      else 
                        select 'Table not exists!';
                      end if;
                    end;
                    call sp_check_table('gb_common_201205152330');

                      select count(1) from information_schema.tables where table_name = p_tablename into @cnt;
                      if @cnt != 0 then 
                        INSERT into gb_2012_05_15_tousu select * from  gb_common_201205151145 where IMSI='460006164215696';
                      else 
                        select 'Table not exists!';
                      end if;
                    end;
                    call sp_check_table('gb_common_201205151145');

                      select count(1) from information_schema.tables where table_name = p_tablename into @cnt;
                      if @cnt != 0 then 
                        INSERT into gb_2012_05_15_tousu select * from  gb_common_201205151145 where IMSI='460009514268101';
                      else 
                        select 'Table not exists!';
                      end if;
                    end;
                    call sp_check_table('gb_common_201205151145');

                        select 'Table not exists!';

                      select count(1) from information_schema.tables where table_name = p_tablename into @cnt;
                      if @cnt != 0 then 
                        INSERT into gb_2012_05_15_tousu select * from  gb_common_201205142315 where IMSI='460023184203643';
                      else 
                        select 'Table not exists!';
                      end if;
